summary: Seeing people being legitimately angry at Dan for being somewhat quiet on all social media is honestly why I think it’s a good...
body:
Seeing people being legitimately angry at Dan for being somewhat quiet on all social media is honestly why I think it’s a good thing that he is doing this. 

He needs a break.   

He needs a break from us. Needs a break from this very very intense fandom that often emotionally depends on him, (myself included).
And I’m sorry, as privileged as it is, that shit can’t be fucking easy having weighing on your shoulders at all times.

So give him this break. He needs to be able to just be, not provide us with content of any kind for once, whether it be tweets, ig stories or videos. 

It really rubs me the wrong way seeing people being actually angry at him, and demanding content, demanding a slice of his life. It’s not like he just disappeared, he gave us a warning, and he will come back. 

I’m not saying don’t be sad, or frustrated, I’m getting slightly antsy and miss seeing his face as well… 

But I wan’t him to take a brake from this fandom, so he can come back and make content he’ll feel good about, and that he feels represents him. And if he lose some followers over this, so be it. 

We are a constant and massive presence in his life, that he can’t escape. 

So give the man a break.
